			</div>

			<div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center space-y-1 mb-8">
				<p>
					&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} zatsit. All rights reserved.
				</p>
				<p>
					Based on <a
						href="https://github.com/API-Green-Score/APIGreenScore"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
